Taylor-

I know we have spoken a few times over the past couple of months regarding exploring
Shift4 as another gateway option for CardConnect. Given some recent developments
(described below), our need to explore alternatives to our current gateway (which is Fiserv)
has become significantly more urgent.

We received notice this afternoon from Fiserv Compliance that they intend to shut down
all *** processing by June 15, 2019.

We will obviously appeal all of this with Fiserv. We were also told last Friday that we are
being delisted from *** at the request of ***. With that said, it is very clear that our
relationship with Fiserv is not in a good place and continuing on our current path doesn't seem
to be a viable option.

Given the above, we would like to begin working with your team immediately to determine
how quickly we can implement Shift4 as a replacement payment gateway for CardConnect.
Please let me know who I should be working with on your side.

Thanks.
